name: Fragmentos vol.1
description:
'Fragmentos vol.1' are part of a new series of beats produced by Yule Aurêh - Made on maschine MK1 and using samples from old records, the EP brings with it a dense atmosphere, the result of a moment of social isolation caused by the pandemic . - by SAMPLEADA LABEL (www.sampleada.com)

beats/mix/artwork: Yule Aurêh (@yuleaureh)
ft bass track 2 / master: Graxaim (@guiceron)
